What you need to know:

The construction of Mzuri Sweets Limited at Kwa Kadzengo along the Mombasa-Malindi highway, which was set to employ more than 1,000 people, is 80 percent complete.The investment, whose owner estimates to cost US$20 million (Sh2 billion), located next to a wetland, had also obtained approvals to backfill the wetland and create an artificial one which would be a recreational park.